Package com.amplitude.skylab

Class Skylab

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplitude.skylab.Skylab
  • public class Skylab
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory class for Skylab. Manages a pool of singleton instances of SkylabClient identified by name. SkylabClient names are normalized to be lowercase. The name "$default_instance" is reserved for the default SkylabClient instance, and is provided for convenience.

    All SkylabClient share the same executor service and http client.
